{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, large language models can be employed to generate descriptive action labels or subtitles, thereby enriching video understanding and applications.",
    "The TAD area can be meticulously optimized in the following ways:",
    "(1) Action description generation: Equipped with powerful natural language processing capabilities, large language models can create highly accurate, natural, and expressive action descriptions.",
    "These descriptions convey the actions in videos with greater detail and precision, enhancing understanding and interpretation of the content.",
    "(2) Contextual understanding and inference: Large language models can perform contextual reasoning and judgment on actions in long videos."
  ]
}